to run after it...

348
00:15:55,268 --> 00:15:58,343
Stop! Stop!

349
00:15:58,866 --> 00:16:00,783
Stop, please, stop.

350
00:16:00,795 --> 00:16:03,231
Stop. Stop the truck.

351
00:16:06,616 --> 00:16:10,273
