354
00:16:19,736 --> 00:16:21,382
My bad.

355
00:16:21,405 --> 00:16:22,761
I'm okay.

356
00:16:25,607 --> 00:16:29,043
Hey, man, thanks for helping me
make my fiancée's Christmas.

357
00:16:29,056 --> 00:16:30,220
No problem.

358
00:16:30,235 --> 00:16:33,533
Too bad I can't deliver all these
packages by the end of the day.

359
00:16:33,545 --> 00:16:37,821
